name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Morty!

name: Agent
line: Rick?

name: Rick
line: Hey, Mooorty.

name: Agent
line: Rick, is everything okay in here?

name: Rick
line: Mooortys are human!

name: Agent
line: All right, Morty, time to make our move.

name: Rick
line: Make it bounce.

name: Agent
line: Allahu  akbar! We're gonna take control of this plane! We got to get out of here and land it on the Pope.

name: Rick
line: What?! We're not gonna land it? We're going to take over the goddamn thing! We just got out of school and we're gonna do it all by yourselves!

name: Agent
line: I thought that was a myth.

name: Rick
line: We're not going anywhere. We're just gonna take over Earth's grossest city!

name: Agent
line: Well, since you're not here to contribute to the discussion, I'll say, "yes."

name: Rick
line: Yeah, well, since this is the first part of a three-pointer, you might as well contribute to it as well.

name: Agent
line: I think it's a good idea, Rick. I think it would be a good learning moment for you.

name: Rick
line: Yes, Rick, if we could get out this whole time, I think we could be a family.

name: Agent
line: You think I could get a job?

name: Rick
line: Oh, geez, Rick! You think I can fly a helicopter?

name: Agent
line: You don't think I would let my boss know I'm putting my kids in a pickle?

name: Rick
line: I don't be a parent, Morty!

name: Agent
line: Oh!
